column5: Though I've seen it and it's good it's not showing here Bernie.
Dang Chris, it shows here.Try it now
Got it now Bernie. Gave me a good idea of where the neighbours bungalows are set up.
Love it Bernie! I assumed it was sunrise but as soon as it got up there I realized it was a sunset flight.

Not too many shacks out this year.Checked with the operators out there today and said there is 20" of ice in most places now. Managed to take a couple loads of firewood across today.Travel is pretty good although a 4X4 would best be used off the road. There are a few drifts.
Ah nothing the old Avenger couldnt handle.LOL  Very cool vid bernie.
That is one cool toy you have there!  Great video Bernie, very serene.
Nice! Looks like the flight skills are coming along
